OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FThe Channel Islands are marking a
OL,7,Fspecial milestone anniversary:
OL,8,Fcelebrating 80 years since the SS Vega
OL,9,Fdocked in Jersey and Guernsey harbours
OL,10,Fto deliver thousands of precious Red
OL,11,FCross parcels.
OL,13,FFrom December 1944, the relief ship
OL,14,Fdelivered more than 100,000 Red Cross
OL,15,Fparcels, helping to keep thousands
OL,16,Falive during the Occupation.
