OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FEach package contained food,
OL,7,Ftoiletries, and medical supplies to
OL,8,Fbolster islanders' diets who had to
OL,9,Fmake do with very little during the
OL,10,FGerman Occupation.
OL,12,FAcross 2024, ITV Channel's Sophie
OL,13,FDulson interviewed five islanders who
OL,14,Frevisited their special memories of
OL,15,Freceiving their parcels.
