OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FHe says: "The whole family used to
OL,7,Fhave a bath in one of the old tin
OL,8,Fbaths and if we could find some wood
OL,9,Fand light a fire, we would warm some
OL,10,Fwater up and all have a turn each.
OL,12,F"My sister would go in first, then by
OL,13,Fage; my elder brother, then me, then
OL,14,Fmy two younger brothers.
OL,16,F"We all shared a bath of water which
OL,17,Fwas - by the time we all got in -
OL,18,Fpretty smelly and grubby."
