OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FFood was also scarce, leaving Peter
OL,7,Fand one of his brothers with no choice
OL,8,Fbut to beg from the Germans.
OL,10,FPeter recalls: "We didn't actually
OL,11,Fspeak to them because we couldn't
OL,12,Fspeak German and most of the young
OL,13,FGermans never spoke English but they
OL,14,Fknew what we were there for.
OL,16,F"Holding our hands out and pointing to
OL,17,Fyour tongue, they knew what we were
OL,18,Fafter.
