OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,F"You're desperate to have something
OL,7,Fbut you've got to get used to the fact
OL,8,Fyou've got nothing to eat - that's how
OL,9,Flife went on."
OL,11,FBut little did Peter know, the
OL,12,Fgreatest gift of all was on its way to
OL,13,FGuernsey. He was almost five when the
OL,14,FSS Vega docked into St Peter Port
OL,15,Fharbour on 27 December 1944.
