OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FFor Peter, it was a day he'll never
OL,7,Fforget, as he explains: "That day was
OL,8,Fabsolutely unbelievable. I mean people
OL,9,Fhad been shut up for five years and
OL,10,Fyet on that day flags appeared - Union
OL,11,FJacks appeared.
OL,13,F"Everybody went absolutely mad. It was
OL,14,Fa really, really joyous day."
