OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FPeter says: "Everybody was handed out
OL,7,Fthese packets of goodies and we didn't
OL,8,Fknow what we were going to find in it.
OL,10,F"Having never seen a piece of
OL,11,Fchocolate, it was unbelievable to have
OL,12,Fsomething sweet in your mouth that you
OL,13,Fcould actually chew and swallow.
OL,15,F"It was really out of this world and
OL,16,Fsomething you couldn't believe."
OL,18,F80 years since Peter received his Red
OL,19,FCross parcel, that sense of disbelief
OL,20,Fis still palpable.
