OL,3,C'It was a really joyous day': Peter
OL,4,CBott's SS Vega memories 80 years on
OL,6,FHe concludes: "I think the Vega really
OL,7,Fsaved a lot of people and without it,
OL,8,FI think Guernsey would have lost a lot
OL,9,Fof its people in the years following
OL,10,Fthe Occupation.
OL,12,F"It was only (the parcels) that
OL,13,Fsustained them when the Occupation was
OL,14,Fover."
